  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Industrial machinery at the bottom of the sea. Wreck body mode at maximum feedback (0.9) creates self-oscillating hull resonance — the comb filter nearly singing on its own. Combined with fast LFO1 (1.5 Hz) modulating the filter cutoff, the result is a rhythmic metallic pumping. Bio exciter at 0.4 mix adds mechanical clicking. The sound of a machine that has been running at the ocean floor for centuries, forgotten by everyone on the surface.",
